'''Hendricks''' is a police officer.

==History==
===Corinne's Arrest===
When [[Corinne Bennett]] was arrested for taking the cash from a convenience store register, Sam went to pick her up. Hendricks met him at the door and brought him in to get her. ''("[[The Time Has Come]]")''

Hendricks brought her to Sam, who asked what she was on. Hendricks said that she was deranged when she came in, so Psych loaded her up. ''("[[Too Much]]")''

==Career==
He's an officer at the country sheriff's department.
